明力不足です。 </p> <p>気をつけてくださいね～♪</p> <p>&nbsp;</p> ";s:6:"photo1";N;s:6:"photo2";N;s:6:"photo3";N;s:6:"access";s:3:"822";s:3:"url";s:75:"http://www.direct-commu.com/colums/business/buisness_001_03_itta-desho.html";s:4:"date";s:19:"2006-10-14 01:23:05";s:2:"id";s:3:"184";}